Class NanoServiceCallbackProxy

  • Object
    • com.tailf.dp.annotations.NanoServiceCallbackProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DpNanoServiceCallback

    public class NanoServiceCallbackProxy
extends Object
implements DpNanoServiceCallback
    Callback proxy for Nano Service Callbacks. Implements the DpServiceCallback interface and delegates calls to the registered callback POJO with annotated methods
